<p>尽管这是两支韩国队伍间的较量，SKT在视野得分上却与SSG相差甚远。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201104/6f3a5e93b3ed44cea1b820363e60a9d9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
